Before investing in gold or a gold mining stock, it is important to check
 where the gold price is from a risk and reward perspective, where are the
 miner's margins in relation to gold and how could changes in the market
 affect gold prices and gold stock prices.
 This approach gives you the answer when considering how can gold and gold
 stocks fit your portfolio.
\end_layout

